---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const lastUpdated = '21 September 2025';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy | Homeless Hounds">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. About This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Homeless Hounds Animal Rescue ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your privacy.
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information
          when you interact with our website and services.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          While we may not be legally required to comply with the Privacy Act 1988 (Cth) as a small
          not-for-profit organization, we voluntarily align with the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs)
          as best practice to protect your information and maintain your trust.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Information -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Contact Information</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-semibold">Homeless Hounds Animal Rescue</p>
          <p>Victoria, Australia</p>
          <p>Email: <a href="mailto:web@homelesshounds.com.au" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">web@homelesshounds.com.au</a></p>
          <p>Website: <a href="https://homelesshounds.com.au" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">homelesshounds.com.au</a></p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Information We Collect -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We collect the following types of personal information:</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Information you provide:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Contact details:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, postal address</li>
          <li><strong>Application information:</strong> Details provided in adoption, volunteer, foster care, surrender, or pet courier applications</li>
          <li><strong>Communication records:</strong> Emails, enquiries, and correspondence with us</li>
          <li><strong>Newsletter preferences:</strong> Your marketing consent and communication preferences</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 mt-4">Information collected automatically:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Technical information:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent on site, referring website</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Essential cookies for site functionality and security (see Section 9)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- How We Use Your Information -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We use your personal information for the following purposes:</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Operational purposes:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Processing and responding to adoption, volunteer, foster care, surrender, and pet courier applications</li>
          <li>Coordinating animal care, adoptions, and related activities</li>
          <li>Communicating with you about your applications or enquiries</li>
          <li>Meeting our legal and regulatory obligations</li>
          <li>Maintaining records for operational and legal purposes</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 mt-4">Marketing purposes (only with your consent):</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Sending newsletters and updates about our rescue activities</li>
          <li>Sharing success stories and adoption opportunities</li>
          <li>Promoting fundraising events and volunteer opportunities</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Direct Marketing -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Direct Marketing</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          We will only send you marketing communications (newsletters and promotional updates) if you have
          explicitly opted in by checking the consent box on our forms or newsletter signup.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Every marketing email we send includes an unsubscribe link. You can opt out at any time by:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Clicking the unsubscribe link in any marketing email</li>
          <li>Emailing us at <a href="mailto:web@homelesshounds.com.au" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">web@homelesshounds.com.au</a></li>
          <li>Using our online unsubscribe form</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          We will process your unsubscribe request within 5 business days. You will continue to receive
          operational emails related to any applications or services you've requested.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Disclosure and International Transfers -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Disclosure and International Transfers</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We may share your personal information with third-party service providers who assist us in
          operating our services. These include:
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Service providers:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Email delivery services:</strong> For sending newsletters and transactional emails</li>
          <li><strong>Website hosting and security services:</strong> Including content delivery and DDoS protection</li>
          <li><strong>Animal management system:</strong> For managing animal records and adoption processes</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 mt-4">
          <p class="text-blue-900">
            <strong>International data transfers:</strong> Some of our service providers store and process
            data outside of Australia, including in the United States. We take reasonable steps to ensure
            these providers handle your information securely, including reviewing their privacy policies,
            security standards, and data protection agreements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Data Security -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information, including:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Encryption of data in transit (SSL/TLS)</li>
          <li>Access controls and authentication (including multi-factor authentication)</li>
          <li>Regular security updates and monitoring</li>
          <li>Limiting access to personal information on a need-to-know basis</li>
          <li>Secure disposal of personal information when no longer needed</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          While we take security seriously, no method of electronic storage or transmission is 100% secure.
          We cannot guarantee absolute security of your information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Data Retention -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We retain personal information only as long as necessary for our operational and legal requirements:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Marketing contacts:</strong> Deleted after 24 months of inactivity or upon request</li>
          <li><strong>Application records:</strong> Retained for 3 years after final outcome</li>
          <li><strong>Financial/donation records:</strong> Retained for 7 years (tax requirements)</li>
          <li><strong>Operational emails:</strong> Retained as needed for record-keeping</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          You can request deletion of your personal information by contacting us. We will comply unless
          we have a legal obligation to retain the information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Cookies -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Cookies and Online Tracking</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We use the following cookies and tracking technologies:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for website functionality and security</li>
          <li><strong>Security verification:</strong> CAPTCHA services to prevent spam and protect forms</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          We do not currently use analytics or advertising cookies. If we add these in the future,
          we will update this policy and provide appropriate consent mechanisms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Your Rights -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">10. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You have the following rights regarding your personal information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete information</li>
          <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your information (subject to legal requirements)</li>
          <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing communications at any time</li>
          <li><strong>Complaints:</strong> Lodge a complaint about our privacy practices</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          To exercise these rights, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:web@homelesshounds.com.au" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">web@homelesshounds.com.au</a>.
          We will respond within 30 days.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Complaints -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">11. Complaints</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          If you have concerns about how we handle your personal information, please contact us first at
          <a href="mailto:web@homelesshounds.com.au" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">web@homelesshounds.com.au</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          If you're not satisfied with our response and believe we are subject to the Privacy Act 1988 (Cth),
          you may lodge a complaint with the Office of the Australian Information Commissioner (OAIC):
        </p>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg mt-4">
          <p>Website: <a href="https://www.oaic.gov.au" target="_blank" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">www.oaic.gov.au</a></p>
          <p>Phone: 1300 363 992</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Children's Privacy -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">12. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Our services are not directed to children under 16. We do not knowingly collect personal
          information from children under 16 without parental consent. If you believe we have collected
          information from a child under 16, please contact us immediately.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Changes to This Policy -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">13. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with
          an updated revision date. For significant changes, we may notify you by email if you've opted
          in to communications.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          By continuing to use our website after changes are posted, you accept the updated Privacy Policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="border-t pt-8 mt-12">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          This Privacy Policy was last updated on {lastUpdated}.
          If you have any questions, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:web@homelesshounds.com.au" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800">web@homelesshounds.com.au</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>